data.description: Beautiful DOUBLE lot with a partial view of Lake Pinehurst- Lots 150 and 165 are being sold together for one price. A small corner of Lot 150, closest to Shamrock Dr., is in the floodplain and unbuildable. However, combining the two lots provides a generous building envelope. Lot dimensions, stated taxes, etc. consist of both lots together. PCC Charter membership is available with buyer to pay transfer fees.
